data.description: Beautiful ranch style home 2000 SF on 5 acres! 3 bed 2 1/2 bath home with new metal roof, 24x24 workshop/garage with electricity. A really nice covered back deck. there is a creek that borders the back of the 5 acres. Nice size kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Nice dining room that overlooks a large great room. You have a second family room with built in shelves and a fireplace. Good size laundry room with a half bath off of it. Nice size master suite and the other bedroom are a good size also. Air purification system installed in December 2022, a/c and septic tank was installed in 2022. A/C was service in the summer 2023. new 40-gal hot water installed September 2023, don't miss out on this Great home!!
